"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 10, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dmp1665702603557.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dmp1665702603557.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dmp1665702603557.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dmp1665702603557\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $keyfields\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"dmp1665702603557___keyfields_271718\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return a list of the fields that make up a primary or candidate key or index.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__topic_d85235e1_d85236e1_d85237e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__p_d85238e1_d85239e1_d85240e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keyfields</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__section_w198ab1b7b5_w199ab1b7_w200ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__p_d85241e1_d85242e1_d85243e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">vList = $keyfields(CUSTOMER, 2)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__topic_d56572e1_d56573e1_d56574e1_d56575e1_d56576e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1141208e91\">\n                       Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__d6103e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__d6103e20__entry__1\">Parameter</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__d6103e20__entry__2\">Data Type</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__d6103e20__entry__3\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dmp1665702603557__d6103e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dmp1665702603557__d6103e20__entry__2\">String</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dmp1665702603557__d6103e20__entry__3\">Entity name.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dmp1665702603557__d6103e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">KeyNumber</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dmp1665702603557__d6103e20__entry__2\">Numeric</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dmp1665702603557__d6103e20__entry__3\"> Key identifier; the value will be\n\t\t\t\t truncated to form an integer. <ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__d6103e80\">1, the primary key.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__d6103e83\">2, 3, 4, and so on, the number that\n\t\t\t\t\t\tidentifies a candidate key that has been defined for <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>. </li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__topic_d56577e1_d56578e1_d56579e1_d56580e1_d56581e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1141208e172\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__li_d34613e1_d34614e1_d34615e1\">String that contains an indexed list of the fields that make up the specified key or index.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__li_d34616e1_d34617e1_d34618e1\">An empty string (\"\") is returned if the referenced entity is a non-database entity, or if an error occurred. <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__table_d8936e1_d8937e1_d8938e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following this\n            Function</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__table_d8936e1_d8937e1_d8938e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__table_d8936e1_d8937e1_d8938e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Error constant</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__table_d8936e1_d8937e1_d8938e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dmp1665702603557__table_d8936e1_d8937e1_d8938e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1102</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dmp1665702603557__table_d8936e1_d8937e1_d8938e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt; </code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dmp1665702603557__table_d8936e1_d8937e1_d8938e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> The entity name provided is not a valid\n\t\t\t\t name or the entity is not present in the component structure. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dmp1665702603557__table_d8936e1_d8937e1_d8938e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1104</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dmp1665702603557__table_d8936e1_d8937e1_d8938e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UPROCERR_KEY&gt;</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dmp1665702603557__table_d8936e1_d8937e1_d8938e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\"> The key number provided is not valid; for\n\t\t\t\t example, the key number was out of range. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__topic_d56582e1_d56583e1_d56584e1_d56585e1_d56586e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1141208e278\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__p_d85253e1_d85254e1_d85255e1\">Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__section_wpq_h3b_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1141208e287\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$keyfields</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"dmp1665702603557__pre_ckd_33b_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">vMaxKeys = $totkeys\nvKeyNum = 1\nwhile (vKeyNum &lt;= vMaxKeys )\n putmess \"Keyfields = %%$keyfields($entname, vKeyNum)%%%\"\n vKeyNum = vKeyNum + 1\nendwhile\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lrk1665702576500.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Validate</a><p>Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jwi1665702576586.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatefield</a><p>Validate a field of the current occurrence.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fdp1665702576817.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>validatekey</a><p>Validate a key of the current occurrence.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526885\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526885\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$keyfields Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 10, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $keyfields Return a list of the fields that make up a primary or candidate key or index. $keyfields ( Entity , KeyNumber ) Example: vList = $keyfields(CUSTOMER, 2) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. KeyNumber Numeric Key identifier; the value will be truncated to form an integer. 1, the primary key. 2, 3, 4, and so on, the number that identifies a candidate key that has been defined for Entity . Return Values String that contains an indexed list of the fields that make up the specified key or index. An empty string (\"\") is returned if the referenced entity is a non-database entity, or if an error occurred. $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 2. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following this Function Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not present in the component structure. -1104 <UPROCERR_KEY> The key number provided is not valid; for example, the key number was out of range. Use Allowed in all component types, except self-contained Reports. Example: Using $keyfields vMaxKeys = $totkeys vKeyNum = 1 while (vKeyNum <= vMaxKeys ) putmess \"Keyfields = %%$keyfields($entname, vKeyNum)%%%\" vKeyNum = vKeyNum + 1 endwhile Copy Related Links Validate Determines whether the valerr data processing attribute is added for the selected entity node in the DTD tree. This attribute holds the occurrence or field validation error (depending on whether the selected item is an entity or field). Valid values are True or False (default). validatefield Validate a field of the current occurrence. validatekey Validate a key of the current occurrence. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}